Author: topcoatsandhats
Text: I’m taking my sister to the waterpark today, and I’ve been p stuck in the battle between starving to look better in the bathing suit, and eating so I have the energy to keep up.  So far I’ve still barely eaten.    My current debate is if I get lunch there or not.  But it’s all high salt foods and idk if I wanna do that kinda thing and get all that water weight so much easier
